Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.78,0:00:18.82,Main,Nitta,0,0,0,,Haló?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.82,0:00:19.57,Italics,Mom,0,0,0,,Yoshifumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.57,0:00:21.27,Italics,Mom,0,0,0,,Čo to bolo za dievča?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:22.13,Main,Nitta,0,0,0,,Dievča?
